### API Integration
The bot uses the CoinGecko API v3:
- **Base URL**: `https://api.coingecko.com/api/v3/`
- **Endpoints**: 
  - `/coins/list` - Get all coins
  - `/simple/price` - Get current prices
  - `/coins/markets` - Get market data

